(309, 36, 64, 11, 'I Could', '', '2006-03-31 00:00:00', 0000, 15, 0, 7, '', '作詞：Cookie\n作曲：Cookie\n\nWe live in a wonderful world, no matter what they say\n\nWe''re so special in this world...in my beautiful world\n\nI wish I could, I know I could\nfind some way, to be different\n\nNothing special in this world, we have to find our way\n\nI could find some way and I will be GOOD\nI could lie on you but can I be good?', 278, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-01-26 00:34:24', '2015-03-12 13:30:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
